reviewText: Our toddler loves this DVD and I have to admit that the songs are quite catchy. After watching this dozens and dozens of times, I still sing along with it. Our toddler asks to watch this several times a day by pointing at the TV, saying "Puh" for puppy, and then panting like a puppy. She's so adorable that I have to give in.
The puppies are super cute but the music is annoying.  The kids don't seem to mind because they play it over and over and over...
